Kaput is a short and dumpy little terrorizer with a brilliant red mohawk, and ZÃƒÂ¶sky is a tall and thin tyrant with a set of yellow antennae. Their exploits almost always end in the same way for the two space tyrants; the two barely escape from their fates by flying off in their dumpy little spaceship, leaving a red smoke trail behind.
